PrecisRegulations Amending the ALBERTA FISHERY REGULATIONS, 1998 by updating the reference to "Director" and defining "mealworm", by banning the practice of archery and the use of spears in fishing for Northern pike, by reducing the number of unattended fishing lines that may be used at any one time, and by allowing maggots and mealworms to be used as bait while fishing for whitefish or perch.
